title: Green d'hide gold-trimmed armour

properties.name: description
properties.value: Green d'hide gold-trimmed armour is a set of Ranged armour that has identical bonuses as Green d'hide armour. Pieces of the armour can be obtained as rewards from medium Treasure Trails. The set consists of only body and chaps.

content:
A player wearing gold-trimmed green dragonhide armour.

Green d'hide gold-trimmed armour is a set of Ranged armour that has identical bonuses as Green d'hide armour. Pieces of the armour can be obtained as rewards from medium Treasure Trails. The set consists of only body and chaps.
